434
01:09:26,531 --> 01:09:30,490
Why in the world would he come
to see Dolly in your absence?

435
01:09:32,537 --> 01:09:34,505
But it did look like his bike.

436
01:09:34,939 --> 01:09:36,907
Come on bro, Kesu's our own.

437
01:09:37,108 --> 01:09:39,508
Why would he run
like a thief on seeing us?

438
01:09:42,547 --> 01:09:45,038
He's in town.
I'll just make him speak to you.

439
01:09:51,355 --> 01:09:54,620
Hello Mental!
Just pass the phone to Kesu.

440
01:09:58,229 --> 01:09:59,662
I see?

441
01:10:03,301 --> 01:10:05,269
Fine then... text me later.

442
01:10:11,576 --> 01:10:12,941
What happened?

443
01:10:13,144 --> 01:10:15,112
God knows! Sonuvabitch's not starting up.

444
01:10:15,580 --> 01:10:17,878
Not the car... what about Kesu?

445
01:10:19,250 --> 01:10:20,547
Kesu?!

446
01:10:20,952 --> 01:10:22,920
There... its started!

447
01:10:23,821 --> 01:10:27,882
Hey Langda! What's the big secret?

448
01:10:32,597 --> 01:10:35,088
Can't believe that was Kesu...

449
01:10:38,603 --> 01:10:44,132
What in the world could he be up to
with Dolly at this hour?

450
01:10:52,617 --> 01:10:53,584
Dolly!

451
01:11:21,345 --> 01:11:23,210
What was Kesu doing here?

452
01:11:31,495 --> 01:11:33,463
