453
01:12:08,499 --> 01:12:09,761
What now?

454
01:12:15,873 --> 01:12:18,103
Speak up! What's so funny?

455
01:12:22,546 --> 01:12:26,778
Every time I look into your eyes,
this single thought crosses my mind.

456
01:12:26,984 --> 01:12:28,451
What thought?

457
01:12:33,624 --> 01:12:41,588
You're either one hell of a fool...
or one hell of a witch.

458
01:12:49,940 --> 01:12:55,810
"O my love..."

459
01:12:57,014 --> 01:13:01,815
"let it last forever today!"

460
01:13:18,335 --> 01:13:21,270
"Come lets still the day!"

461
01:13:21,939 --> 01:13:25,238
"Lets chase the sun away!"

462
01:13:25,809 --> 01:13:33,272
"Keep the shadows at bay... O my love!"

463
01:13:39,857 --> 01:13:44,794
"O my love...

464
01:13:47,064 --> 01:13:51,194
"Let me scold you whilst
you pretend to get scared..."

465
01:13:53,337 --> 01:13:56,204
"let my love fall
in sweet tears from your eyes..."

466
01:13:57,174 --> 01:13:59,802
"my body stitched to yours..."

467
01:14:01,011 --> 01:14:03,002
"turn your back and
you will tear me to shreds..."

468
01:14:03,180 --> 01:14:05,148
"I will take you away with me...
my body your soul"

469
01:14:05,382 --> 01:14:08,146
"Where I end and you begin"

470
01:14:11,121 --> 01:14:16,149
"O my love..."

471
01:14:18,529 --> 01:14:25,162
"let it last forever today!

472
01:14:29,273 --> 01:14:31,764
Now tell me... why am I a fool?

473
01:14:34,612 --> 01:14:39,242
Cos' what's a gorgeous girl like you
doing with a brute like me?!

474
01:14:41,218 --> 01:14:43,118
And witch?

475
01:14:48,826 --> 01:14:51,795
Cos' at times I feel, deep down,

476
01:14:52,029 --> 01:14:54,793
