482
01:18:22,239 --> 01:18:23,399
Cheetah?

483
01:18:28,946 --> 01:18:31,073
Wolf?

484
01:18:38,455 --> 01:18:39,752
Serpent?

485
01:18:47,130 --> 01:18:48,256
Chamaeleon?

486
01:18:50,534 --> 01:18:54,436
Nope... You are my bunny rabbit!

487
01:19:05,916 --> 01:19:07,884
What would you like for dinner?

488
01:19:14,091 --> 01:19:16,059
I'd like to drink some blood.

489
01:19:28,305 --> 01:19:36,144
"Wake up little princess!"

490
01:19:44,021 --> 01:19:48,754
