491
01:19:49,293 --> 01:19:53,161
"Eyes that hold me in their spell."
"May I never be away from their sight!

492
01:19:58,335 --> 01:20:06,765
"The dawn blushes pink on your cheek"

493
01:20:09,313 --> 01:20:14,273
