494
01:20:19,489 --> 01:20:24,791
"Your sweet flesh beckons
Comes hither a bee to tickle you"

495
01:20:25,162 --> 01:20:29,792
"Come now my darling wake up."

496
01:20:29,967 --> 01:20:34,802
"Ask for your heart's desire,
I give my word in blood"

497
01:20:35,372 --> 01:20:39,138
"Just for this once... open your eyes"

498
01:20:42,346 --> 01:20:44,314
Here! I'm up.

499
01:20:45,115 --> 01:20:47,140
Can I really ask for anything?!

500
01:20:48,986 --> 01:20:50,817
Think again.

501
01:20:55,392 --> 01:20:57,360
Forgive Kesu this one time.

502
01:21:09,006 --> 01:21:12,271
What happened?

503
01:21:12,909 --> 01:21:15,776
That's not possible!
- But why?!

504
01:21:18,815 --> 01:21:23,775
If I let him off lightly,
he'll never learn in this lifetime.

505
01:21:24,988 --> 01:21:26,956
So you'll be pissed
with him all your lifetime?

506
01:21:35,165 --> 01:21:38,134
Next time please don't
make any false promises!

507
01:21:47,010 --> 01:21:49,205
"I give my word in blood"

508
01:21:53,450 --> 01:21:55,975
Fine. I'll forgive him
on the wedding day.

509
01:22:00,190 --> 01:22:02,488
Do I call the priest then?
Meanie...?

510
01:22:07,964 --> 01:22:12,264
According to the charts, the 3rd month
of our calendar is an auspicious time.

511
01:22:12,936 --> 01:22:15,769
What date will that be?
- The 30th of next month.

512
01:22:21,344 --> 01:22:24,108
Did you hear?!
The 30th of next month is...

513
01:22:24,347 --> 01:22:26,315
...the auspicious date for the wedding...

514
01:22:26,483 --> 01:22:32,115
which means Kesu gets your favor
in exactly 5 weeks!

515
01:22:32,522 --> 01:22:34,786
Kesu gets his pardon in 5 weeks!

516
01:22:37,327 --> 01:22:39,295
She seems happier with the forgiving
than with the wedding... isn't it?

517
01:22:43,266 --> 01:22:45,791
Dolly really dotes on our Kesu.

518
01:22:48,004 --> 01:22:54,136
They've known each other a long time?
- They both went to the same college.

519
01:22:55,378 --> 01:22:58,814
No wonder!

520
01:23:04,387 --> 01:23:06,287
No wonder what?!

521
01:23:07,791 --> 01:23:12,285
Nothing nothing!
Me and my filthy mind... that's all.

522
01:23:14,164 --> 01:23:19,431
Langda! Tell me what's on your mind!

523
01:23:22,227 --> 01:23:26,357
No... its just that
Dolly's such a stunner...

524
01:23:27,299 --> 01:23:32,362
and you know how Kesu is!
Bloody flirt!

525
01:23:33,972 --> 01:23:37,931
Just wondering if he ever had
any designs on her?

526
01:23:40,378 --> 01:23:43,347
On second thoughts,
what a silly idea!

527
01:23:46,918 --> 01:23:54,882
Kesu is a sweet soul but
he strays around too much... bloody slut!

528
01:23:56,428 --> 01:24:01,559
It won't be a bad idea brother if we keep
a close watch on Dolly till the wedding.

529
01:24:02,734 --> 01:24:08,502
The world is full of big bad wolves
and our Dolly is too too naive!

530
01:24:27,025 --> 01:24:28,856
Brother Kichlu!

531
01:25:39,564 --> 01:25:42,226
Patience son...

532
01:25:46,237 --> 01:25:48,228
We should lie low till the polls.

533
01:25:51,076 --> 01:25:53,374
If we keep silent,
we'll be labelled cowards.

534
01:25:54,913 --> 01:25:58,371
Indore Singh's days are numbered!

535
01:26:01,453 --> 01:26:08,825
Fine... at least wait till
your wedding's past.

536
01:26:11,229 --> 01:26:12,321
Wedding?!

537
01:26:12,530 --> 01:26:16,830
Hmm... isn't there
a date for next month?

538
01:26:18,203 --> 01:26:20,364
How did you get to know?
- I told him.

539
01:26:23,475 --> 01:26:25,500
The way you people dashed off
the other day,

540
01:26:26,211 --> 01:26:28,839
I got really worried.

541
01:26:29,881 --> 01:26:33,840
I called for Kesu and
thankfully he got me here.

542
01:26:44,295 --> 01:26:45,853
Good show!

543
01:27:07,185 --> 01:27:10,313
First stop Kichlu,
then goes Indore Singh.

544
01:27:12,090 --> 01:27:15,321
Langda... you hit town
and sniff out Kichlu.

545
01:27:17,062 --> 01:27:24,833
Mental! Take Babulal's help and
get me Indore Singh's final itinerary.

546
01:27:45,056 --> 01:27:46,853
Anything for Kesu, bro?

547
01:27:50,228 --> 01:27:52,196
Somebody's got to hand out
the wedding invites!

548
01:28:17,322 --> 01:28:19,222
Can't you see...!
I'm on the phone...

549
01:28:51,222 --> 01:28:54,350
Your pain is your own...
for no one else to see...

550
01:28:55,593 --> 01:28:57,857
The truth is no matter
how much I assure you,

551
01:28:58,429 --> 01:29:08,498
I won't be able to understand
your suffering.

552
01:29:12,377 --> 01:29:15,813
Wait a sec!
Bloody mother of...!

553
01:29:16,581 --> 01:29:18,549
What a brainwave, Sir Langda!

554
01:29:21,586 --> 01:29:24,987
Why don't you hunt down Kichlu
instead of me?!

555
01:29:27,025 --> 01:29:30,153
Just drop him in Omi's lap.

556
01:29:32,130 --> 01:29:38,831
Kichlu's gone underground, but if
you wish, you can get to him in a flash.

557
01:29:40,538 --> 01:29:42,028
Ask how?

558
01:29:42,307 --> 01:29:44,502
Ask how?!
- How?

559
01:29:45,009 --> 01:29:47,307
That Billo Chamanbahar of yours...

560
01:29:47,946 --> 01:29:50,176
She's the ace private dick of our trade.

561
01:29:55,153 --> 01:29:58,020
Had bought it for Indu,
but you gift it to Billo.

562
01:30:02,060 --> 01:30:05,359
But this looks very expensive, brother?

563
01:30:05,563 --> 01:30:08,862
If it can help a friend,
its worth is priceless!

564
01:30:10,201 --> 01:30:13,534
Brother Langda...
you are a true friend...

565
01:30:17,575 --> 01:30:21,534
Come come... Don't be shy!

566
01:30:22,380 --> 01:30:25,349
Kesu doesn't hold anything to heart,
likes giving it on the face.

567
01:30:32,390 --> 01:30:33,880
Will you have a small one?

568
01:30:34,125 --> 01:30:36,889
Moron! Forgotten that
day's thrashing or what?

569
01:30:38,296 --> 01:30:42,392
But what do we do about the wedding cards?
- Rajju will hand them out.

570
01:30:46,604 --> 01:30:48,572
Won't you, pretty polly?

571
01:30:48,940 --> 01:30:54,901
And this won't be the first time
you'd be doing it... eh...!

572
01:31:02,420 --> 01:31:04,911
The sun is going to rise
from the south tomorrow.

573
01:31:07,892 --> 01:31:09,860
Why so?

574
01:31:11,262 --> 01:31:18,862
First you took me to the multiplex...
bought me popcorn and lunch,

575
01:31:19,070 --> 01:31:21,868
Then ice cream at the lake...
topped with a walk on the mall road.

576
01:31:24,242 --> 01:31:29,339
Its time to call it a night
yet you're not dragging me to bed...

577
01:31:30,648 --> 01:31:32,548
What's the big idea?

578
01:31:37,989 --> 01:31:39,957
I'm tired Billo.

579
01:31:43,061 --> 01:31:44,892
I've tired you out... no?

580
01:31:45,063 --> 01:31:50,399
Nope... its my loneliness...

581
01:31:58,076 --> 01:32:00,044
You haven't answered me yet.

582
01:32:03,381 --> 01:32:04,575
What?

583
01:32:09,153 --> 01:32:11,018
Will you marry me?

584
01:32:19,849 --> 01:32:22,977
Are you nuts?!
All this marriage talk!

585
01:32:23,886 --> 01:32:26,480
Remember the saying 'Horses without reins
don't get lassoed easily!'.

586
01:32:27,256 --> 01:32:34,162
This is not a joke Billo...
I'm tired of all this straying.

587
01:32:35,698 --> 01:32:39,498
It all seems futile.
Just want to settle down with you now.

588
01:32:48,077 --> 01:32:50,045
Got something for ya...

589
01:32:57,553 --> 01:33:01,011
Still don't quite get it...

590
01:33:04,560 --> 01:33:08,018
Anyway, you've managed to impress me.

591
01:33:13,569 --> 01:33:14,536
Swine!

592
01:33:16,705 --> 01:33:18,468
My adorable swine!

593
01:33:20,709 --> 01:33:23,007
At least now tell me
what your scheme is?!

594
01:33:29,251 --> 01:33:36,987
"My tongue longs to taste the spice...
The spice of your love!"

595
01:34:10,226 --> 01:34:15,528
"Lover I can never get enough...
The spice of your love!"

596
01:35:01,010 --> 01:35:06,505
"They all tease me...
this gang of rakish cops."

597
01:35:06,715 --> 01:35:12,017
"They spoil me with their gifts...
the grocers on my street."

598
01:35:13,055 --> 01:35:17,788
"Big spender... spend a penny on me."

599
01:35:18,494 --> 01:35:22,794
"A sweet lick of honey from your fingers...
Grant me."

600
01:35:24,500 --> 01:35:29,460
"Your spice leaves me gasping...
smoldering me to death."

601
01:35:41,850 --> 01:35:49,484
"I spent the night craving...
The spice of your love!"

602
01:36:16,552 --> 01:36:24,459
"My brute... your breath
tunes me up like a flute."

603
01:36:33,302 --> 01:36:40,208
"Your passion can make me
do anything that you can imagine."

604
01:36:48,183 --> 01:36:50,481
"At times they sip from your eyes...

605
01:36:50,853 --> 01:36:53,981
Later they want to drink
from your lips."

606
01:36:56,692 --> 01:37:02,494
"Sometimes it feels nice to die...
Sometimes its too painful to live."

607
01:37:04,700 --> 01:37:13,506
"I toss and turn all night. Is that
my lover who tiptoes to my bedside?"

608
01:37:15,844 --> 01:37:20,907
Your spice leaves me gasping...
smoldering me to death.

609
01:37:36,165 --> 01:37:43,970
"My lover... let me have a bit
The spice of your love!"

610
01:39:33,015 --> 01:39:34,448
Lets go, bro!

611
01:39:36,151 --> 01:39:37,516
Lets go!

612
01:39:37,686 --> 01:39:39,654
Take Billo and vanish
for a day or two!

613
01:39:40,255 --> 01:39:42,450
We'll meet directly
at the village for the wedding.

614
01:39:45,727 --> 01:39:47,456
2 am in the morning?

615
01:39:47,663 --> 01:39:50,461
Ya man... middle of the bloody night!

616
01:39:50,666 --> 01:39:52,657
Tring Tring... Tring Tring...

617
01:39:53,502 --> 01:39:57,461
I immediately went for my gun...
but the 'General' promptly stops me!

618
01:39:58,040 --> 01:40:03,945
Smiling wickedly,
he says "It must be Billo"

619
01:40:05,247 --> 01:40:07,977
And lo and behold! The doors open.

620
01:40:08,183 --> 01:40:14,486
Enters a fuming Billo Chamanbahar...
strung like Lord Rama's bow!

621
01:40:15,324 --> 01:40:19,784
On seeing her temper, I immediately tucked
my head in and pretended to be asleep.

622
01:40:25,200 --> 01:40:27,100
Somebody come and pump this.

623
01:40:27,736 --> 01:40:30,432
But as my good luck would have it,
there was a hole in the quilt.

624
01:40:31,840 --> 01:40:36,106
Now I'm human after all...
and a little perverted at that.

625
01:40:39,815 --> 01:40:41,442
It was a cold winter night!

626
01:40:41,650 --> 01:40:43,447
Kesu starts getting all horny
but Billo doesn't even let him peck her!

627
01:40:46,488 --> 01:40:48,456
Kesu then takes out this glittering
jewel from the box...

628
01:40:49,491 --> 01:40:51,459
this sparkling gorgeous waistband!

629
01:40:51,660 --> 01:40:56,962
Glittering gold jewels!
Never seen anything so beautiful!

630
01:40:57,666 --> 01:40:59,463
No way?
- Yeah...!

631
01:41:02,170 --> 01:41:06,971
The way the waistband glowed in the dark,
you'd never need a lamp again in your life!

632
01:41:07,175 --> 01:41:09,006
Then?
- What do you think then?!

633
01:41:09,177 --> 01:41:11,475
The waistband was all
she was left wearing!

634
01:41:11,847 --> 01:41:13,815
Both sang nonstop duets till the morning!

635
01:41:14,016 --> 01:41:15,984
Creak! Creak!

636
01:42:00,829 --> 01:42:03,457
Forgive Kesu!

637
01:42:03,665 --> 01:42:06,463
I called for Kesu and
thankfully he got me here.

638
01:42:07,502 --> 01:42:09,970
Kesu gets his pardon in 5 weeks!

639
01:42:16,511 --> 01:42:19,969
What took you so long?

640
01:42:24,519 --> 01:42:26,487
I had been waiting for you...

641
01:42:28,824 --> 01:42:30,815
Why weren't you taking my calls?

642
01:42:37,265 --> 01:42:40,496
It was on silent mode... sorry...

643
01:42:42,871 --> 01:42:44,839
Want some dinner?
- No!

644
01:42:46,808 --> 01:42:48,833
I'll go get some water.

645
01:42:51,546 --> 01:42:53,514
What happened?

646
01:42:54,883 --> 01:42:56,851
Where is the waistband?

647
01:42:58,086 --> 01:42:59,178
Sorry?

648
01:43:03,892 --> 01:43:05,519
The waistband!

649
01:43:06,561 --> 01:43:09,029
Oh... must be lying around here...

650
01:43:10,565 --> 01:43:12,863
Here or elsewhere?!

651
01:43:14,036 --> 01:43:16,004
Must be in the house somewhere.

652
01:43:17,172 --> 01:43:19,640
Fine. Go put it on.

653
01:43:24,646 --> 01:43:26,637
Don't be naughty now!
Wait till the wedding.

654
01:43:28,250 --> 01:43:30,480
I asked you to go put it on!

655
01:43:34,523 --> 01:43:37,651
And I... asked you to wait
till the wedding!

656
01:43:38,927 --> 01:43:41,487
Now... means now... dammit!

657
01:44:02,884 --> 01:44:06,012
Haven't you kept the token
of my love real carefully?!

658
01:44:08,290 --> 01:44:11,191
Maybe the chest gobbled
it up or was it the famished almirah?

659
01:44:17,966 --> 01:44:22,130
A generations old heirloom, and it
takes you precisely three days to lose it!

660
01:44:32,514 --> 01:44:34,982
Sure you haven't gifted it away?

661
01:44:38,687 --> 01:44:40,985
Who in the world
will I gift it to... Omkara?

662
01:44:44,192 --> 01:44:46,160
Who do I have besides you anyway?

663
01:44:53,935 --> 01:44:56,563
Have left my whole world to be with you!

664
01:45:08,083 --> 01:45:16,047
"The wood burns into charred coal...

665
01:45:30,906 --> 01:45:38,870
"My heart burns into emptiness."

666
01:45:41,516 --> 01:45:46,476
"Don't burn my heart away...

667
01:45:49,057 --> 01:45:52,823
"Don't pawn my heart away."

668
01:46:13,848 --> 01:46:19,809
Now what?!
The sun's also started getting up late!

669
01:46:24,693 --> 01:46:28,857
Not bad! Looks like someone
didn't get any rest all night!

670
01:46:33,301 --> 01:46:36,964
Save up some of that passion
for your wedding night, my princess!

671
01:46:41,042 --> 01:46:43,010
What happened now?!

672
01:46:46,248 --> 01:46:48,148
Speak up!

673
01:46:52,854 --> 01:46:55,982
If you keep crying like this,
you'll flood the whole village!

674
01:46:57,692 --> 01:47:03,494
Oh! Missing your papa... are you?

675
01:47:05,967 --> 01:47:07,935
Sober up now dodo!

676
01:47:09,271 --> 01:47:11,239
I'll take care of you.

677
01:47:11,873 --> 01:47:14,501
I'll be your pa, ma, bro, sis...

678
01:47:16,077 --> 01:47:18,443
everything rolled into one...
now stop crying!

679
01:47:21,216 --> 01:47:23,446
What's this now?!

680
01:47:25,220 --> 01:47:27,450
Did you fall somewhere?

681
01:47:29,924 --> 01:47:31,892
Did Omi hit...?!

682
01:47:37,532 --> 01:47:39,796
You just wait here!
That sonuvabitch...!

683
01:47:42,971 --> 01:47:45,462
Hit me out of love...

684
01:47:49,811 --> 01:47:53,474
I'll tell you a little secret.

685
01:47:55,517 --> 01:48:02,980
My grandma always told me to keep
these men slightly hungry.

686
01:48:06,795 --> 01:48:12,825
Else the day they get satisfied, they'll
puke you out like nobody's business!

687
01:48:15,270 --> 01:48:16,931
Got that!

688
01:48:18,473 --> 01:48:24,434
Now... that's a rare smile in this weather!
About time! Forever thirsty... this guy!

689
01:49:22,470 --> 01:49:24,438
It's Babulal!

690
01:49:38,486 --> 01:49:42,445
Where's he going running off to now?

691
01:49:42,657 --> 01:49:48,960
It's inauspicious to leave
in the middle of the ceremony son...

692
01:49:58,740 --> 01:50:01,140
It burns me up!

693
01:50:02,243 --> 01:50:06,475
Ooh! Aah! It burns me up!

694
01:50:07,248 --> 01:50:11,810
The train's left the station.
Indore Singh's in the fourth wagon...

695
01:50:15,056 --> 01:50:16,956
Will you drink some?

696
01:50:19,928 --> 01:50:22,419
What's Kesu up to nowadays?

697
01:50:23,598 --> 01:50:24,792
God only knows!

698
01:50:24,966 --> 01:50:28,766
Every time you call him,
his phone is permanently out of LBW...

699
01:50:31,606 --> 01:50:33,574
But Dolly will surely know
his whereabouts.

700
01:50:34,642 --> 01:50:36,940
They are constantly in touch
over the phone.

701
01:50:40,215 --> 01:50:41,443
Langda!

702
01:50:43,218 --> 01:50:44,947
Yes brother.

703
01:50:46,821 --> 01:50:48,812
Will you tell me the truth?

704
01:50:50,492 --> 01:50:54,451
Ya bro, of course I will!

705
01:50:56,498 --> 01:51:00,457
I want a clear-cut yes or no.

706
01:51:01,836 --> 01:51:03,963
Of course! Please to ask!

707
01:51:08,543 --> 01:51:10,841
Is there anything going on
between Kesu and Dolly?

708
01:51:18,620 --> 01:51:20,918
May my tongue fall off
before I utter another word!

709
01:51:23,591 --> 01:51:25,923
Yes or no?

710
01:51:27,996 --> 01:51:29,691
I regard you more than my life...
forgive me...

711
01:51:29,864 --> 01:51:31,991
Yes or no?!

712
01:51:34,869 --> 01:51:37,429
Don't be so cold blooded
with your own brother.

713
01:51:39,908 --> 01:51:42,172
Yes or no?

714
01:53:46,701 --> 01:53:48,669
Game, set and match!

715
01:53:50,738 --> 01:53:52,501
Let's leave!

716
01:53:59,280 --> 01:54:01,009
Yes or no?

717
01:54:07,555 --> 01:54:09,523
Yes or no?!

718
01:54:12,927 --> 01:54:18,456
Yes or no?!

719
01:54:19,233 --> 01:54:20,461
No...!

720
01:54:32,046 --> 01:54:35,140
That's what you wanted to hear?! No!

721
01:54:39,520 --> 01:54:42,216
Do you have the courage
to hear the truth?

722
01:54:46,594 --> 01:54:48,562
What truth do you want to know?

723
01:54:49,530 --> 01:54:52,829
That during the Kichlu episode,
when I stayed over at Kesu's house...

724
01:54:53,935 --> 01:54:57,496
I heard him mutter in his sleep

725
01:54:57,705 --> 01:55:02,506
"Dolly... if our love has to live,

726
01:55:03,010 --> 01:55:06,502
we'll have to hide it
from the entire world."

727
01:55:14,956 --> 01:55:17,857
Was there any other witness there?

728
01:55:18,960 --> 01:55:20,120
No!?

729
01:55:26,667 --> 01:55:28,965
When you see your dreams...
you see it alone.

730
01:55:29,971 --> 01:55:32,462
When you hear your dreams...
you hear it alone.

731
01:55:33,908 --> 01:55:38,868
When I look into Dolly's eyes,
your entire Bible sounds phony!

732
01:55:40,982 --> 01:55:43,815
Now go get some proof before the
wedding... understood?!

733
01:55:44,919 --> 01:55:52,883
And if you don't, I'll wring
your corpse limp... Bastard!

734
01:56:05,673 --> 01:56:08,506
What the...?! Stop this racket!

735
01:56:29,931 --> 01:56:34,459
Who are you playing here for...
is it the Lord's wedding...?

736
01:56:36,504 --> 01:56:38,472
Take all your shebang
and come to our place...

737
01:56:38,973 --> 01:56:40,941
the girl's house.

738
01:56:47,815 --> 01:56:49,612
And isn't it Rip Van Winkle himself?

739
01:56:51,052 --> 01:56:53,020
What do you think you're up to, eh!?

740
01:56:53,688 --> 01:56:55,656
Come home... there's lots to be done.

741
01:56:59,827 --> 01:57:02,489
Get a bath and do something
about your lovely face!

742
01:57:03,798 --> 01:57:06,995
As if it wasn't pretty enough,
Sir's gone and had a facial in the city!

743
01:57:10,905 --> 01:57:12,839
Bitch and a half!

744
01:57:28,656 --> 01:57:30,453
The horse's here.

745
01:57:31,492 --> 01:57:33,460
Start dressing it up.

746
01:57:40,001 --> 01:57:46,133
When I woke up this morning, saw the word
'fool' tattooed on my forehead.

747
01:57:48,042 --> 01:57:53,981
Do what I say... else you'll find the word
'moron' tattooed tomorrow morning.

748
01:58:00,288 --> 01:58:02,483
"Don't you want Dolly... eh...?"

749
01:58:36,190 --> 01:58:38,124
That's enough anger
for a lifetime Omi bro!

750
01:58:38,492 --> 01:58:41,950
Today you have to keep
your word and pardon me.

751
01:58:44,999 --> 01:58:48,958
Hey! Don't set up
the barbecue near the loo!

752
01:58:49,704 --> 01:58:54,471
Take it away...
who the hell's in charge here?

753
01:59:04,518 --> 01:59:05,485
Kesu?

754
01:59:05,953 --> 01:59:07,921
Kesu's not here. Who's on the line?
- Billo

755
01:59:08,856 --> 01:59:12,485
Billo ma'am!

756
01:59:13,260 --> 01:59:15,820
Kesu's occupied right now.

757
01:59:16,197 --> 01:59:17,926
Call him on the phone

758
01:59:18,132 --> 01:59:21,101
I'm sorry... we're not allowed
to disturb him.

759
01:59:21,469 --> 01:59:23,437
I said just call him

760
01:59:24,205 --> 01:59:26,435
As I've already explained,
we're not allowed inside.

761
01:59:26,807 --> 01:59:28,934
The room is locked tight.

762
01:59:33,647 --> 01:59:35,444
Who's there with him?

763
01:59:38,019 --> 01:59:42,922
Can't tell you the truth.
And my lies won't assure you.

764
01:59:44,825 --> 01:59:50,457
Hello Hello... any message?

765
02:00:57,832 --> 02:01:00,960
Don't be a fool!
It's just a bogus omen.

766
02:01:02,703 --> 02:01:06,799
Don't let it bother you...
stop crying!

767
02:01:08,008 --> 02:01:10,476
It's not nice to be mourning
on your wedding day.

768
02:01:11,879 --> 02:01:13,847
Lets get you dressed now.

769
02:01:15,583 --> 02:01:17,483
Will you get ready now
or should I call Omkara?

770
02:01:18,986 --> 02:01:20,920
Should I?!

771
02:01:22,823 --> 02:01:24,791
Call him if you please!

772
02:01:25,493 --> 02:01:29,759
At least I'll get to know what is the
grave sin that I've committed?

773
02:01:31,665 --> 02:01:36,432
This is not the same Omkara for whom
I gave up home and hearth.

774
02:01:38,873 --> 02:01:42,832
My Omkara used to shield me
in his palms like a precious petal.

775
02:01:48,649 --> 02:01:50,446
What happened... but?

776
02:01:51,652 --> 02:01:55,588
I don't know...
he's always annoyed at me

777
02:01:57,691 --> 02:02:00,455
That day I lied that
he'd hurt me out of love.

778
02:02:05,699 --> 02:02:08,463
He hit me because
I misplaced something.

779
02:02:10,638 --> 02:02:11,696
What thing?

780
02:02:11,906 --> 02:02:16,138
Whatever it is, you don't
have right to hit anyone!

781
02:02:19,847 --> 02:02:23,146
You once lost Golu at the fair!
Did I utter a word?

782
02:02:29,023 --> 02:02:31,491
It's time I had a word with him.

783
02:02:33,527 --> 02:02:35,495
Don't worry

784
02:02:36,530 --> 02:02:38,498
Look here dodo!

785
02:02:38,899 --> 02:02:41,993
Men and women have always
had a pan and ladle equation.

786
02:02:42,937 --> 02:02:47,499
Alone, they stay miserable...
and together, they make one helluva racket!

787
02:02:48,075 --> 02:02:51,511
Cling Clang Cling Clang!

788
02:02:54,548 --> 02:02:56,516
Not Bad!

789
02:02:57,985 --> 02:03:00,510
Now... that's a rare smile in this weather!

790
02:03:16,036 --> 02:03:18,129
For our silver jubilee anniversary,

791
02:03:18,505 --> 02:03:23,135
I took my wife to Timbuktu!
- Timbuktu?!

792
02:03:24,511 --> 02:03:26,638
What're you planning now
for the 50th year celebrations?

793
02:03:27,314 --> 02:03:29,475
Thinking of getting her back from Timbuktu!

794
02:03:35,189 --> 02:03:37,089
Now it's my turn to crack one.

795
02:03:37,291 --> 02:03:39,486
Now that's a joke in itself!

796
02:03:43,530 --> 02:03:46,158
There was this man who once got married.

797
02:03:49,903 --> 02:03:50,995
Then?

798
02:03:52,773 --> 02:03:54,502
That was the end of it.

799
02:04:03,717 --> 02:04:08,518
You can lie to the whole world but
I don't get fooled that easy.

800
02:04:11,558 --> 02:04:14,186
Your eyes give it away...

801
02:04:17,698 --> 02:04:19,666
Won't share it with your own sister?

802
02:04:21,235 --> 02:04:23,465
What demons are you
carrying around in your head?

803
02:04:34,581 --> 02:04:37,982
Her father's voice keeps ringing
in my ears all the time...

804
02:04:44,525 --> 02:04:50,486
"She who can dupe her own father
will never be anyone's to claim"

805
02:04:58,539 --> 02:05:01,508
Two faced character... no?

806
02:05:07,948 --> 02:05:11,509
When the scriptures themselves
have sullied women,

807
02:05:14,755 --> 02:05:17,451
who can blame mere mortals
like you, brother?

808
02:05:20,994 --> 02:05:28,457
We renounce our homes and walk into
your lives with bare empty hands.

809
02:05:36,176 --> 02:05:38,474
But even after the holy fires
approve us,

810
02:05:40,080 --> 02:05:43,481
we're regarded disloyal
sooner than loyal.

811
02:05:48,889 --> 02:05:50,857
There's time yet, brother!

812
02:05:54,862 --> 02:06:00,823
If you have the slightest of doubts,
please do not stoop to attend the marriage!

813
02:06:03,537 --> 02:06:06,506
We'll take care of Dolly...
you don't worry about her fate.

814
02:06:35,502 --> 02:06:40,838
If I don't get the proof I'll make sure
he never misses his father.

815
02:09:44,157 --> 02:09:45,454
Ya?

816
02:09:45,659 --> 02:09:47,627
Billo's looking for you in the village.

817
02:09:52,499 --> 02:09:56,458
At this hour?
- Ya... she seems to be in one foul mood.

818
02:09:57,838 --> 02:09:59,806
I sent her to Langda bro.

819
02:10:01,508 --> 02:10:03,476
I think you should call him.

820
02:10:13,987 --> 02:10:16,751
Ya Kesu?
- Is Billo around?

821
02:10:16,990 --> 02:10:18,958
Ya she's upstairs.

822
02:10:20,160 --> 02:10:24,426
Your sweetheart's
not looking very happy, I fear.

823
02:10:24,731 --> 02:10:27,757
God knows why
the bitch's always in heat?!

824
02:10:28,669 --> 02:10:30,762
This blasted affair!

825
02:10:31,605 --> 02:10:33,903
What affair?

826
02:10:35,208 --> 02:10:39,110
This 'love affair'
is a bloody bore!

827
02:10:40,147 --> 02:10:43,947
The 'wham bang' days
were much better!

828
02:10:44,951 --> 02:10:50,947
If she's so turned on before the wedding,
imagine how she'll devour me after?

829
02:10:52,826 --> 02:10:59,789
I told her we should avoid doing it
on the wedding night... but no luck!

830
02:11:06,840 --> 02:11:08,808
You here?!

831
02:11:09,509 --> 02:11:11,477
Who are you flirting with...
this late at night?

832
02:11:13,013 --> 02:11:15,846
Don't you dare disconnect!
Finish your damn love chat!

833
02:11:16,049 --> 02:11:17,744
You're misunderstanding the whole thing.

834
02:11:17,984 --> 02:11:23,422
Ya right! I've understood you enough!
You are a compulsive womanizer!

835
02:11:24,458 --> 02:11:27,427
Given a chance, you'd take
Your own mother to bed!

836
02:11:27,728 --> 02:11:30,424
That'll be enough!
Shut your mouth!

837
02:11:32,265 --> 02:11:36,599
Whose wife did you strip this away from?
- Billo... listen to me for a minute!

838
02:12:36,930 --> 02:12:38,557
Sorry honey... we're finished!

839
02:12:41,268 --> 02:12:42,895
Don't get crazy, girl!

840
02:12:43,537 --> 02:12:47,496
Wait... listen up please!

841
02:12:50,210 --> 02:12:52,838
Do we have to do this?

842
02:13:13,900 --> 02:13:16,198
Lets go now, please!

843
02:13:20,841 --> 02:13:25,471
Won't you wait for dessert, my friend?

844
02:13:30,050 --> 02:13:33,850
Go stiff him a couple from point blank,

845
02:13:34,988 --> 02:13:38,151
else the 'ex-General'
will suffer all night.

846
02:13:41,995 --> 02:13:43,826
Go Champ!

847
02:14:18,832 --> 02:14:20,800
Your lover's history!

848
02:14:21,868 --> 02:14:22,960
What?

849
02:14:23,703 --> 02:14:25,466
Your lover...

850
02:14:27,841 --> 02:14:29,468
Kesu...

851
02:14:30,710 --> 02:14:33,474
Poor soul couldn't
even carry your keepsake.

852
02:14:37,050 --> 02:14:39,018
Where did you get this
blasted thing?

853
02:14:49,896 --> 02:14:52,490
Hey meanie!

854
02:14:55,902 --> 02:14:57,870
Stop play acting now.

855
02:15:02,075 --> 02:15:04,043
You've been stripped naked.

856
02:15:11,251 --> 02:15:13,219
Your 'innocence' makes me want to puke.

857
02:15:24,831 --> 02:15:26,799
Since when have you been
warming Kesu's loins?

858
02:15:34,174 --> 02:15:42,138
OK... at least tell me when was
the first time you slept with him?

859
02:15:44,784 --> 02:15:47,150
Just for the record?
Are you carrying his baby by any chance?

860
02:15:55,662 --> 02:16:01,828
See... the deal is - accept it,
I'll spare you your life.

861
02:16:16,049 --> 02:16:18,779
Thanks for the offer but...

862
02:16:22,822 --> 02:16:24,790
you are free to take my life.

863
02:16:39,039 --> 02:16:41,007
Did I lack anything?

864
02:16:42,509 --> 02:16:43,476
Huh?

865
02:18:49,569 --> 02:18:52,538
Omi bro!

866
02:18:56,176 --> 02:18:59,145
Omi bro! There's been a lot of bloodshed,
please rush!

867
02:18:59,679 --> 02:19:01,647
Omi brother... are you listening?!

868
02:19:38,151 --> 02:19:40,779
She looks so childlike in her sleep...

869
02:19:45,525 --> 02:19:51,953
She who can dupe her own father
will never be anyone's to claim.

870
02:20:02,575 --> 02:20:04,509
Two faced character!

871
02:20:18,658 --> 02:20:20,592
I stole this.

872
02:21:04,971 --> 02:21:06,461
Brother Omi!

873
02:21:20,153 --> 02:21:21,745
Go home.

874
02:21:23,990 --> 02:21:25,958
Go home you bitch!

875
02:21:26,993 --> 02:21:28,858
Didn't you hear me... whore?!

876
02:21:29,028 --> 02:21:30,086
Langda!

877
02:21:47,814 --> 02:21:49,441
She's lying Omi bro...

878
02:21:52,251 --> 02:21:54,219
God knows why she wants me dead!

879
02:21:55,655 --> 02:21:57,623
Seems she too is having an affair...

880
02:22:01,494 --> 02:22:03,962
I regard you more than God!
I'd never...

881
02:22:17,677 --> 02:22:20,976
Think what you must.

882
02:22:23,583 --> 02:22:28,816
My truth and my lies have
all got blurred.

883
02:22:31,691 --> 02:22:36,993
Go shoot me in the head! Release me!

884
02:22:51,544 --> 02:22:53,512
Death will only help free your body...

885
02:22:56,015 --> 02:22:58,848
...but our souls are forever damned...

886
02:23:02,722 --> 02:23:08,524
We won't find redemption...
not in this life!

887
02:24:31,511 --> 02:24:36,471
"Wake up little princess!"

888
02:24:36,849 --> 02:24:40,808
Your eyes like sweet petals!

889
02:24:42,188 --> 02:24:47,148
"Eyes that hold me in their spell."

890
02:24:47,693 --> 02:24:51,493
"May I never be away
from their sight!"

891
02:24:52,532 --> 02:25:00,496
"My little princess...
my sleeping doll wake up."

892
02:25:06,546 --> 02:25:11,506
"Wake up little princess!"

893
02:25:11,784 --> 02:25:15,515
"Your eyes like sweet petals!"

894
02:25:28,000 --> 02:25:35,463
"The dawn blushes pink on your cheek"

895
02:25:38,511 --> 02:25:43,471
"Craving to caress you...
come now wake up...

896
02:25:46,719 --> 02:25:51,486
"Your sweet flesh beckons
Comes hither a bee to tickle you"

897
02:25:52,258 --> 02:25:56,490
"Come now my darling wake up."

898
02:25:57,530 --> 02:26:02,490
"Ask for your heart's desire
I give my word in blood"

899
02:26:02,868 --> 02:26:06,497
"Just for this once... open your eyes"

900
02:26:07,540 --> 02:26:14,503
"My little princess...
my sleeping doll wake up."

901
02:26:15,681 --> 02:26:20,778
"Wake up little princess!
Your eyes like sweet petals!"

902
02:26:40,506 --> 02:26:42,474
Open the door, Omi Bro!

903
02:26:56,689 --> 02:27:00,489
How did you ever think...?

904
02:27:07,900 --> 02:27:09,868
Hush now!

905
02:27:11,871 --> 02:27:13,839
One more word and its all over.

906
02:27:15,541 --> 02:27:22,447
Isn't it all over anyway?

907
02:27:39,298 --> 02:27:42,461
No, it isn't over yet.

908
02:27:44,704 --> 02:27:49,664
Forgotten how I pasted
the Army Guy in court?

909
02:27:53,045 --> 02:27:55,479
Bang on the temple... Boom!

910
02:27:57,516 --> 02:27:59,484
And our friend Indore Singh?

911
02:28:00,219 --> 02:28:04,815
Shoved the gun right
up his mouth and... Boom!

912
02:28:08,060 --> 02:28:10,028
And Thakur?

913
02:28:11,530 --> 02:28:13,498
Right through his heart....

